mon Prayer","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1705202,"age":68,"year":"1558","julianDay":2290108,"title":"Act of Uniformity","description":"The Act of Uniformity was passed by the Parliament of England and required all people to go to church once a week. The consequence of not attending church was a fine of 12 pence, which was a considerable amount for a poor person.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"Sir William Kythin was born in 1490, in Lancashire, England. He married Isabel Budden Majors in 1532, in Leicestershire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died on 10 March 1562, in Cassington, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 72."},"et":{"1490–10 March 1561/62":"1490–10. märts 1562","1492–Female":"1492–Surnud","1512–1560":"11.jaanuar1512kuni10.jaanuar1513–1560","1490–1562":"1490–1562","12 August 1560":"22. august 1560","1558":"1558","1512":"11. jaanuar 1512 kuni 10. jaanuar 1513","1532":"1532","1562":"1562","1560":"1560","10 March 1561/62":"10. märts 1562","1492":"1492","1490":"1490","1549":"1549","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Cassington, Leicestershire, England":"Leicestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cossington, Leicestershire, England":"Cossington, Leicestershire, England","Cassington, Oxfordshire, England":"Cassington, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1490–10 March 1561/62":"1490–10. maaliskuuta 1562","1492–Female":"1492–Kuollut","1512–1560":"vuodesta11.tammikuuta1512vuoteen10.tammikuuta1513–1560","1490–1562":"1490–1562","12 August 1560":"22. elokuuta 1560","1558":"1558","1512":"vuodesta 11. tammikuuta 1512 vuoteen 10. tammikuuta 1513","1532":"1532","1562":"1562","1560":"1560","10 March 1561/62":"10. maaliskuuta 1562","1492":"1492","1490":"1490","1549":"1549","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Cassington, Leicestershire, England":"Leicestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Cossington, Leicestershire, England":"Cossington, Leicestershire, England","Cassi